title.rendered: Ground Basement Triplex For Sale In Defence Colony

content.rendered:
This 325 square yards property boasts 4 bedrooms with attached bathrooms, a spacious open-plan living area, an Italian modular kitchen, stylish washrooms, modern interiors, and wide attached balconies on each floor. The property is facing the award-winning best park of Defence Colony which is the most sought-after location. it has luxury amenities like a private elevator with a separate lift lobby, an exclusive driveway, parking space for 4 cars, a fully developed basement, etc.
This property is enviably located in Defence Colony which is known to be one of the wealthiest colonies in New Delhi. Residents here are mostly known businessmen and retired and active army personnel.
☀️Defence Colony
☀️325 sq yds
☀️5000 sq ft Built-up area
☀️Basement + Ground Floor + Stilt Triplex
☀️Park Facing
☀️Separate Gates
☀️4 Car Parking Space
☀️Exclusive Driveway
☀️Private Elevator
☀️4BHK
☀️Ultra Luxury property
☀️Excellent Sales Service
☀️Reputed Builder
📞 Call On 9818312077 For Site Visit
☀️ Follow @royalerealtorsindia on social media
